TITLE: Basic PlayCanvas Example Template
DESCRIPTION: Basic template for creating a new PlayCanvas example with canvas initialization and application setup
SOURCE: https://github.com/playcanvas/engine/blob/main/examples/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import * as pc from 'playcanvas';

const canvas = /** @type {HTMLCanvasElement} */ (document.getElementById('application-canvas'));
window.focus();

const app = new pc.Application(canvas, {});

export { app };
```

